3-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Giro-Trixter-and-Havoc-mountain-bike-gloves-one-piece-AX-suede-microfiber-palm-MTB-3-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Giro-Trixter-and-Havoc-mountain-bike-gloves-one-piece-AX-suede-microfiber-palm-MTB-3-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>White snow wasn’t the best backdrop to photograph the very white palm of the new Trixter, but the perforation and touchscreen details help it stand out. While the Trixter uses a one piece, pre-curved microfiber palm, it isn’t the AX Suede material found on their more expensive gloves. Still, it feels good on the hand, and offers an ultra thin bar-feel.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Giro-Trixter-and-Havoc-mountain-bike-gloves-one-piece-AX-suede-microfiber-palm-MTB-2.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Giro-Trixter-and-Havoc-mountain-bike-gloves-one-piece-AX-suede-microfiber-palm-MTB-2.jpg\" alt=\"Trixter MTB glove fourchettes\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Giro-Trixter-and-Havoc-mountain-bike-gloves-one-piece-AX-suede-microfiber-palm-MTB-2.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Giro-Trixter-and-Havoc-mountain-bike-gloves-one-piece-AX-suede-microfiber-palm-MTB-2.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Giro-Trixter-and-Havoc-mountain-bike-gloves-one-piece-AX-suede-microfiber-palm-MTB-2-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/upload